.git
# D9 (FEN-2051 / audit FEN-2034): the gateway fan-out + stress harness
# (apps/gateway/load/, ~2.5k lines + captured result JSON) is DEV TOOLING — no
# runtime image ever imports it. It stays in the repo as a living harness, but is
# excluded from every build context so `COPY apps/gateway` in the gateway
# Dockerfile cannot bake it into the prod image.
apps/gateway/load
# Never bake env files into an image — at the root OR nested (e.g.
# apps/convex/.env.local, which carries a CONVEX_DEPLOYMENT that breaks the
# self-hosted deploy — FEN-78 #3). The `**/` globs cover every subdirectory.
.env
.env.*
**/.env
**/.env.*
!.env.example
!**/.env.example
*.log
data
redis-data
